UC Davis


MyAdmissions









MyAdmissions allows you to check the status of your UC Davis application and, if you are admitted, submit your Statement of Intent to Register and complete your required pre-enrollment tasks.






Account Login
Before you can access the site, you must set up a UC Davis Login ID and password.
